  QuestId: Trial of Weaving
  QuestTitle: Trial of Weaving
  QuestObjective: Cast 5 Spells
  QuestDescription: 'A presence settles over you, cool and patient. "The threads
    of power flow through all things. Show that you may grasp them without becoming
    entangled."


    You are encouraged to cast five spells. Any spells. Harmless
    or harmful makes no difference.'
  QuestOutcome: "There is a stillness after each incantation, as though the world
    itself pauses to listen.\n\nWhen the fifth spell leaves your lips, the silence
    lingers a moment too long\u2014heavy with quiet calculation."
  MaxProgres: 5
